column2: This spreadsheet documents the datasets in use by the CURRENT version of MortalityMinder (0.01 Beta) and its loaders. Most datasets are located in MortalityMinder/data. All loaders are located in MortalityMinder/init. Datasets are not limited to these - contact infrastructure team or create a pull request to the GitHub Repository to have new datasets and/or loaders added to the project.
